  "explanation": "<section id=\"explanation\">\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Proactive</span> To znači preduzeti korake rano ili rešiti situaciju pre nego što postane problem. Primer:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Being proactive means fixing small issues before they become big problems.</span> - Ovde, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">proactive</span> se tiče preduzimanja koraka ranije.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Approach</span> je način za rešavanje nekog problema. Na primer:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Her approach to solving the problem was very effective.</span> - Ovde, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">approach</span> se odnosi na način koji je koristio da reši problem.</li>\n</ul>\n</section>",
